iberate the people of the state from poverty, hardship and hunger. “Time has come for the people to have a purposeful leadership that will turn around the economy of the state for the benefit of the people,” he added. Vanguard The quest for the Benue State Government has begun in earnest between the incumbent, Governor Samuel Ortom of the PDP and Mr. Emmanuel Jime of the All Progressives Congress, APC. October 13, 2018 In "News" The Abuja Division of the Federal High Court, on Friday, ordered the All Progressives Congress, APC, not to take any step to organise indirect governorship primary election in Kogi State, pending the determination of a suit that was lodged before the court by some chieftains of the party in the… August 9, 2019 In "News" ABUJA—The constitutional crisis trailing the Kogi State governorship election took a new twist, yesterday, with All Progressives Congress, APC members of the Kogi State House of Assembly insisting that Mohammed Audu, the first son of the deceased APC Candidate, Prince Abubakar Audu, should replace his father in the December 5… November 28, 2015 In "News"